DescDetail: <<
KColorChooser is a color palette tool, used to mix colors and create
custom color palettes. Using the dropper, it can obtain the color of any
pixel on the screen. A number of common color palettes are included,
such as the standard Web colors and the Oxygen color scheme.
<<
DescUsage: <<
Use cursor to pick a color from the palette.
Does not work for picking colors outside of the app window.
<<
